T02TD2386E:19b-1: ma h'a y'a na aa pa t'a ra n'a ma /
T02TD2386E:19b-3: theg pa chen po'i gnas lugs gtan la 'bebs pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2386E:19b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2386E:19b-5: theg pa chen po'i bdag nyid ni //
T02TD2386E:19b-6: bde chen rgya mtsho'i bdud rtsi ni //
T02TD2386E:19b-7: mtha' dbus mnyam pa'i tshad nad sel //
T02TD2386E:19b-8: dga' ba che la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2386E:19b-9: theg pa rnams kyi mchog gyur pa //
T02TD2386E:19b-10: shes dang shes bya'i ye shes ni //
T02TD2386E:19b-11: gzhan la phan phyir rang la min //
T02TD2386E:19b-12: bdag gis gtan la dbab par bya //
T02TD2386E:19b-14: so so'i las dang rnam par ldan //
T02TD2386E:19b-15: dngos po gzugs can 'ching ba'i rgyu //
T02TD2386E:19b-16: phyi dang nang gi gzugs med pas //
T02TD2386E:19b-17: de nyid ma grub gnyis med do //
T02TD2386E:19b-18: gang zhig 'dzin pa gzugs yin te //
T02TD2386E:19b-19: 'dzin pa med pas de nyid do //
T02TD2386E:19b-20: de ni dam pa'i ye shes te //
T02TD2386E:19b-21: lhun grub kha dog dbyibs dang bral //
T02TD2386E:19b-22: mkhas pa rnams kyis rang rig rtogs //
T02TD2386E:19b-23: gang zhig rig pa stong pa de //
T02TD2386E:19b-24: stong pa min la rig pa min //
T02TD2386E:19b-26: bden gnyis bral ba'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD2386E:19b-27: stong nyid rig pa'i lta ba 'di //
T02TD2386E:19b-28: snying rje chen po'i shes rab bo //
T02TD2386E:19b-29: rdzogs pa'i rim dang lha sgrub sogs //
T02TD2386E:19b-30: rgyud rnams kun las gsungs pas kyang //
T02TD2386E:19b-31: de nyid don dam ye shes min //
T02TD2386E:19b-32: don dam ye shes stobs kyis ni //
T02TD2386E:19b-33: rdzogs pa'i lha ni grub par 'gyur //
T02TD2386E:19b-34: de phyir bdag ni rdo mkhan dhis //
T02TD2386E:19b-35: blo dman rnams kyi yul min pa //
T02TD2386E:19b-36: don dam kun rdzob gnyis med bshad //
T02TD2386E:19b-37: theg pa chen po'i gnas lugs gtan la 'bebs pa zhes bya ba slob dpon chen po rdo mkhan dhis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
